{"tid":359084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[鄰國]深圳地鐵乘客跑落車爆恐慌 網民：以為炸彈抱頭踎低","createTime":"2017-08-14T08:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T11:25:39.000Z","uid":51271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4cfe9cfb14fcd299590990340d9c5c8fd886ed22","tid":359084,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:12:37.000Z","msg":"遲早一次踩死幾十人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170814/57079323\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170814%2F57079323&d=2%2FWHG351XZVBiXPaDmUC%2FghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=dbb65e18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170814%2F57079323&h=c077da5e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170814/57079323</a><br />\n<br />\n 深圳地鐵不足一個月又發生人撞人事件！1號線列車昨晚9時32分左右，停靠科學館站時，車廂內一名男乘客突然跑動，導致其他乘客慌亂下車。地鐵職員立即將該趙列車清空，並在現場安撫乘客情緒。深圳地鐵在官方微博表示，事件中沒有乘客受傷。<br />\n<br />\n有網民昨日微博發影片問：「深圳地鐵科學館大逃亡？」「邊跑邊喊，炸彈，砍人，製造恐慌，本來也沒啥事，莫名其妙的就被謠言給踩踏了。」「我以為是恐怖事件，炸彈之類的還抱頭蹲下。」<br />\n<br />\n深圳地鐵提醒，在車廂相對封閉的環境，遇到突發事件首先應保持冷靜，不要盲從、急躁，先觀察或反饋求助，有乘客慌亂時，及時的提醒也非常必要，如有必要儘速報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170814/large/1502690993_d15e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170814%2Flarge%2F1502690993_d15e.jpg&h=46b94d02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f10472b004ef2b17bfa6462021b1be27f959df06","tid":359084,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:17:50.000Z","msg":"渣架<br />\n大陸乜野都識爆，一早訓練充足都好驚"},{"pid":"6a247ef3596bd428abe5b0f38e7fb0bd2a221d65","tid":359084,"uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:18:17.000Z","msg":"只要一大班人係深圳狂跑，一定全巿恐荒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5814ac69281ae63b32e9febe3b76f1b918587eda","tid":359084,"uid":112622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:20:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f740b3af8ceda3b045cc4bd97acb546ec22bbc29","tid":359084,"uid":80294,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:20:57.000Z","msg":"真係唔怪得中共放咁錢去維穩<br />\n<br />\n成個社會根本已經爛晒<br />\n<br />\n只要有少少火頭 隨時一觸即發"},{"pid":"a94ff107c9808732e5db803372669610210ed392","tid":359084,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係成日恥笑人地有恐襲架咩?"},{"pid":"6eb44a36141aa581b66c75a343c9ddd4836d13bf","tid":359084,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:22:26.000Z","msg":"唔使跑，大叫一聲話唔定都可以搞到人踩人"},{"pid":"24f101fd18f39bdcda9d365b5fb4f93aefe6f6d4","tid":359084,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:24:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係唔怪得中共放咁錢去維穩<br />\n<br />\n成個社會根本已經爛晒<br />\n<br />\n只要有少少火頭 隨時一觸即發</blockquote><br />\n所以點解香港維穩咁舒服 <br />\n<br />\n俾個論壇班憤青屌下就得"},{"pid":"4a15a5e7b6ef95c75f4ab2b8ef21af852dafd30a","tid":359084,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:25:43.000Z","msg":"明明深圳無發生過咩大型恐襲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b039d651daec4f0961b7c53a46442b386f8f4675","tid":359084,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:27:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明深圳無發生過咩大型恐襲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港有人咁做，應該啲人都係拎著新電話影條傻佬"},{"pid":"ef42a8c340338a3f6db8b5cd6da6f4a313223a32","tid":359084,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:28:28.000Z","msg":"又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條友可能急屎啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img